        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer931224515" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17127713093132027657">This is a suspenseful, mystery novel that loses its punch midway through and, as the violence piles up, loses its believability. Iles created characters that are so worn and clichéd: the heroes being the white, liberal lawyer and newspaper reporter; the villains being southern, white, uneducated bubbas. I found his portrayal of black, female sexuality especially objectionable and stereotypical.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


